headline: Agilent xCELLigence RTCA Instrumentation Applied in Recent FDA Approval
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., March 24, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) is pleased to announce its role in supporting Autolus Therapeutics’ FDA approval for AUCATZYL®, a recently approved CAR T therapy. Agilent's advanced cell analysis instrumentation, specifically the xCELLigence Real-Time Cell Analysis (RTCA) technology, was applied in developing and validating AUCATZYL.
